about.summary: A portable, lightweight MessagePack serializer and deserializer written in pure Python.

name: u-msgpack-python
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "u-msgpack-python" %}
{% set version = "2.5.2" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 09c85a8af77376034396681e76bf30c249a4fd8e5ebb239f8a468d3655f210d0

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - umsgpack

about:
  home: "https://github.com/vsergeev/u-msgpack-python"
  license: "MIT"
  license_family: "MIT"
  license_file: "LICENSE"
  summary: "A portable, lightweight MessagePack serializer and deserializer written in pure Python."
  dev_url: "https://github.com/vsergeev/u-msgpack-python"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tschoonj
